165886785430812597.Text: Two large bipedal creatures native to Vvardenfell are dangerous predators. The alit and the kagouti are similar in appearance, but the alit is smaller, and the kagouti has a distinctive bony neck shield. They are both savage hunters, and quite dangerous.
